(371, 'Prancing Pony Pagan\'s Empire', 'An ’Imperial’ pale ale brewed with spelt and rye, and hopped with three varieties of U.S hops.', 198, 3, 'https://res.cloudinary.com/ratebeer/image/upload/w_120,c_limit,d_beer_icon_default.png,f_auto/beer_488567.jpg', 488567),
